title: 111: Embracing Immaturity | Ear Biscuits Ep. 111
description:
Rhett & Link sit down with Ten Feet Tall's Mike & Alex to talk growing old but not up, what moments changed their perceptions of self the most, and the Ten Feet Tall creative process on this episode of Ear Biscuits.
